OL,7,FA west Belfast mother has said her 13-
OL,8,Fyear-old son, Daire, is being failed
OL,9,Fby a lack of services for ADHD in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland, as calls mount for
OL,11,Fthe Department of Health to commission
OL,12,Fservices and a strategy here.
OL,14,FDaire was diagnosed with autism in
OL,15,FPrimary 3 but his mum began to see
OL,16,Ftraits of ADHD too as he got older.
