OL,7,FKaren says she brought Daire to his GP
OL,8,Fbefore the Covid-19 pandemic and that
OL,9,Fhe was given a referral but years
OL,10,Flater, she found out it wasn't
OL,11,Fprocessed and that he is now too old.
OL,13,FThe reality is there is little help
OL,14,Ffor anyone with suspected ADHD in
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland, especially over the
OL,16,Fage of 11.
OL,18,FSome turn to charity ADD NI, who
OL,19,Fthemselves are dealing with a backlog
OL,20,Fof over 4,000 people.
