OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FAlliance MLA Peter McReynolds has
OL,8,Flaunched a petition calling for the
OL,9,FDepartment of Health to commission
OL,10,FADHD services here, including a
OL,11,Fstrategy for treatment.
OL,13,FIn response, a spokesperson for the
OL,14,FDepartment said: "Any decision to
OL,15,Fcommission Adult ADHD services in the
OL,16,Ffuture will be based on an assessment
OL,17,Fof the level of demand for services,
OL,18,Fand in the context of future budget
OL,19,Favailability.
