OL,7,F"Officials from the Department are
OL,8,Fconsidering the future direction of
OL,9,Ftravel for the commissioning of Adult
OL,10,FADHD services and how best to progress
OL,11,Fthe issue, in discussion with relevant
OL,12,Fstakeholders.
OL,14,F"Subject to future budget
OL,15,Favailability, potential next steps
OL,16,Finclude the commissioning of research/
OL,17,Fanalysis of adult ADHD demand to
OL,18,Finform options for future
OL,19,Fcommissioning strategies, as well as a
OL,20,Fregional workshop to explore potential
OL,21,Fways forward."
